  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil half a kettle</p><p>Cut your<strong> potatoes </strong>(skins on) into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a large baking tray (cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1666000773739-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1666000773739-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1666000773739-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1666000773739-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1666000773739-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice your<strong> red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>diced onion</strong> to a small heat-proof bowl and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong> to soften for 5 min</p><p>Once softened, drain and return to the bowl with your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled onion</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1666000778238-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1666000778238-x400.jpg",
