    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a medium sized pot over a medium-low heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a knob of<strong> butter</strong> <strong>alternative</strong></p><p>Once melted, add your<strong> ginger & garlic paste </strong>and cook for 30 secs</p><p>Add 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span><strong> flour </strong>to the pot with your <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and stir everything together with a wooden spoon until a thick paste forms</p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
