      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pot from the heat and gradually whisk in your <strong>creamy single soy</strong>, a little at a time</p><p>Return the pot to a low heat and cook for 4-5 min or until a smooth, creamy sauce remains – this is your <strong>creamy curry sauce</strong></p>",
